thread.title: Moody, Owls roll against McCollum
thread.title_full: Moody, Owls roll against McCollum - San Antonio Express-News

author: Ben Baby
title: Moody, Owls roll against McCollum
text:
There only seemed to be one thing Highlands senior Bruce Moody couldn’t do on Thursday night.
The running back lined up a few yards away from the goal line on a couple point-after attempts against McCollum and couldn’t find a way into the end zone. But it’d be hard to hold that against him considering the performance he had at Alamo Stadium.
Moody scored early and often to help the Owls salt away a 32-14 victory against McCollum in District 28-5A. Moody scored four times in the first half and finished with 299 yards and five touchdowns.
